# General Rules

Small project rules. Add new sections as conventions are adopted.

## Plain Text Conventions

Use common ASCII characters in all text: code, comments, docs, and commit messages.

- **No m-dashes:** Use a normal hyphen (`-`) instead of an em-dash or en-dash
- **No special unicode:** Use ASCII equivalents for punctuation (e.g. curly apostrophe `'` -> straight `'`, smart quotes -> straight `"` and `'`)
